# Where the explorer fetches memory assets. Default /api/asset = the dynamic
# route that streams public/memories/ from disk (so live-drop splats written
# after `next build` are served, which Next's static public/ handler won't do).
# Point at a static host / CDN for deployment. See config/explorer.ts.
NEXT_PUBLIC_MEMORIES_BASE_URL=/api/asset

# S3 — where uploads are copied for the curator's manual SHARP run.
# Point this at S1's input folder on the GPU box for the exhibition.
# RECON_INBOX=../samples/input
